378
00:32:28,762 --> 00:32:31,557
That a small-sized shelter was there.

379
00:32:31,682 --> 00:32:33,289
Hold on a second.

380
00:32:33,472 --> 00:32:37,697
Then does it mean they got an order from the giant sphere...

381
00:32:38,313 --> 00:32:41,879
