412
00:34:33,053 --> 00:34:35,076
Sungjin High instead of Hamil High.

413
00:34:37,142 --> 00:34:38,837
And another high after that.

414
00:34:49,903 --> 00:34:51,046
Gosh.

415
00:34:54,363 --> 00:34:57,806
